result.name: 2001-2003-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-north-sea-sediment-particl
result.notes:
Particle Size Analysis (PSA) for seabed sediment samples collected in the 
North Sea during three Cefas cruises on RV Corystes (Cruise Codes CORY 
10/2001, CORY 09/2002 and CORY 8x/2003) as part of a study on sediment 
biogeochemistry under Defra project A1224 in the period 2001 - 2003.
